, 比記者圍住"},{"pid":"32890a0d823b5ff3cb137e8fc0ca9f1b9efae530","tid":1260180,"uid":4597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:03:34.000Z","msg":"明報不明，信報不信"},{"pid":"22cb101fb6d65f03330723ae85c939dd06ef04bf","tid":1260180,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死 無証話係便衣"},{"pid":"e3c42b45018446dd44797cb1942ad41eca85cc32","tid":1260180,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cb101fb6d65f03330723ae85c939dd06ef04bf","tid":1260180,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死 無証話係便衣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf75eb10641573cccb68f3a031d598df142631b1","tid":1260180,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:08:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1259875/page/6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1259875/page/6</a><br />\n<br />\n入黎睇睇幫手推下,唔該"},{"pid":"19915be3140d941edbc72982f885fcfe80c4a01f","tid":1260180,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【事實】灰衫警沒帶委任證衝向警總鐵閘並持起棍狀物件。在場人士一度以為其身份為示威者，幸沒有示威者跟隨。最後總部內警員開閘護送進入。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其他示威者亦 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>合 理 懷 疑</strong></span> 該名警員企圖帶動示威者衝擊警總。</span><br />\n<br />\n頭先copy一位巴打 大家請廣傳"},{"pid":"3960dc1324604a4340a57c1a6aacc728fb8d5ea9","tid":1260180,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:18:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f245a0a3d422bfc600c247750e83f2c87ba95bca","tid":1260180,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b1253f6c47a3479fad96ca2f4fe6444141e261cb","tid":1260180,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:26:55.000Z","msg":"明報仲差過東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b067c40e9646e182e4fb2c44c9a0ece1a5c6a72","tid":1260180,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:27:37.000Z","msg":"黃底警員利用警察身份， 打開 警署閘門， 企圖帶領示威者進入 警察總部，幸好一眾示威者還有理性先無釀成慘劇，快啲成立獨立調查委員會， 徹查此事！<br />\n<br />\n一眾示威者在警署門外要求釋放黃絲警員， 絕不容許警員帶有黃外思想， 成立獨立調查委員會事不容緩😔😔😔<br />\n<br />\n女絲屍警員在網上支持示威者衝擊警署😡 可恥😤 快點成立獨立調查委員會徹查內奸<br />\n<br />\n譴責黃絲休班警帶頭衝擊警總， 要求成立獨立調查委員會， 找出黃底內奸， 我要真香港警察💪<br />\n<br />\n黃絲警員帶頭衝擊警署， 建議快速成立獨立調查委員會， 撇除內奸， 還警隊一個清白🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\n尊重警員自身政治立場，強烈譴責黃絲警員衝擊警察總部🤬🤬🤬<br />\n<br />\n黃底休班警煽動示威者衝擊 內鬼警察失當行為 企圖撕裂社會 聽命外國爪牙 破壞社會安寧😰<br />\n<br />\n藍絲page洗板用"},{"pid":"6962d83403a297f21b2ffc82e947f09e012b0413","tid":1260180,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/vb.258224170919874/336694817229659/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftang.earthquake%2Fvideos%2Fvb.258224170919874%2F336694817229659%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=dc7f770d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/vb.258224170919874/336694817229659/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n有片有真相"},{"pid":"0b186c8b43f49779c633f113a1893d4131b02417","tid":1260180,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"雖然一早投左共，<br />\n但我都想知如果查生仲在生佢會點諗"}]}